<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink103-kilavi">
        aṟattoṭu niṉṟatōḻi atu vaṟpuṟuppāṉ vēṇṭic cevilikkuc colliyatu</p>
      <p xml:lang="en">
        Spoken by the confidante who stood with the truth to the foster mother, the courageous man [= hero] (?) desiring that. </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink106">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻi vēṇ ṭaṉṉai yavarnāṭṭut</l>
<l>tutikkā laṉṉan tuṇaicettu mitikkun</l>
<l>taṇkaṭal vaḷaiyiṉu milaṅkumiva</l>
<l>ḷaṅkali ḻākaṅ kaṇṭici ṉiṉaintē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>  Oh mother, please mother, If you look, having thought [about it],</l>
<l>Her pretty, shining body will shine even more than the conches</l>
<l>On the cool ocean in his land upon which </l>
<l>The goose [with] quivering legs steps, thinking that [it was its] mate.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
